{"kanda":6,"sarga":84,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"राममाश्वासयानेतुलक्ष्मणेभ्रातृवत्सले ।निक्षिप्यगुल्मान् स्वस्थानेतत्रागच्छद्विभीषणः ।।6.84.1 ।।","trans":"As Lakshmana was comforting his affectionate brother, Vibheeshana came to Rama assigning the troops to reach their respective places.","words":[{"d":"भ्रातृवत्सले","m":"affectionate brother"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणे","m":"by Lakshmana"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama आश्वासमाने comforting"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"गुल्मान्","m":"troops"},{"d":"स्वस्थाने","m":"to their respective places"},{"d":"निक्षिप्य","m":"assigning"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"आगच्छत्","m":"came"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"नानाप्रहरणैर्वीरैश्चतुर्भिस्सचिवैर्वृत: ।नीलाञ्जनचयाकारैर्मातङ्गैरिवयूथप","trans":"Accompanied by the four ministers surrounded by four ministers resembling leaders of elephants, who looked dark like collyrium, Vibheeshana came to highsouled Rama. He witnessed Vanaras whose eyes were filled with tears.","words":[{"d":"नानाप्रहरणैः","m":"different kinds of weapons"},{"d":"नीलाञ्जनचयाकारैः","m":"dark in colour like collyrium"},{"d":"यूथप:","m":"troops"},{"d":"मातङ्गैःइव","m":"like elephants"},{"d":"चतुर्भिः","m":"four"},{"d":"सचिवै","m":"ministers:"},{"d":"वृतः","m":"surrounded"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"शोकलालसम्","m":"given to grief"},{"d":"महात्मानम्","m":"great soul"},{"d":"राघवम्","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"अभिगम्य","m":"reached"},{"d":"बाष्पपर्याकुलेक्षणान्","m":"eyes full of tears"},{"d":"वानरांश्चापि","m":"Vanaras also"},{"d":"ददृशे","m":"witnessed"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"राघवं च महात्मानमिक्ष्वाकुकुलनन्दनम् ।ददर्शमोहमापन्नंलक्ष्मणस्याङ्गमाश्रितम्","trans":"He (Vibheeshana) saw the great soul, the delight of the Ikshvaku race deluded, distressed, and lying on the lap of Lakshmana.","words":[{"d":"महात्मानम्","m":"great soul"},{"d":"इक्ष्वाकुलनन्दनम्","m":"delight of Ikshvaku race"},{"d":"मोहम्","m":"deluded"},{"d":"आपन्नम्","m":"distressed"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणस्य","m":"Lakshmana's"},{"d":"अङ्कम्","m":"lap"},{"d":"आश्रितम्","m":