":"हितचिकीर्षुणा","m":"for his welfare"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"वैदेहीम्","m":"Vaidehi"},{"d":"उत्सृजस्व","m":"return"},{"d":"इति","m":"this"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"न कृतवान्","m":"not done"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"नैवसाम्ना न दानेन न भेदेनकुतोयुधा ।साद्रष्टुमपिशक्येतनैवचान्येनकेनचित्","trans":"\"She can't be perceived by recourse, by charity, by dissension or even by war. Why again any other means. There is no chance.\"","words":[{"d":"सा","m":"she"},{"d":"साम्ना","m":"by recourse"},{"d":"द्रष्टुम् अपि","m":"perceived"},{"d":"न शक्येत","m":"not possible"},{"d":"दानेन","m":"by charity"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"भेदेन","m":"by dissension"},{"d":"न","m":"no"},{"d":"युधा","m":"by war"},{"d":"कुतः","m":"do"},{"d":"अन्ये","m":"any other"},{"d":"केनचित्","m":"why again"},{"d":"नैव","m":"no chance"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"वानरान्मोहयित्वातुप्रतियातः स राक्षसः ।मयामयींमहाबाहोतांविद्दिजनकात्मजाम्","trans":"That Rakshasa by hoodwinking the Vanaras withdrew from the battlefield. O mighty armed one! Killing of Janaki is an illusion.","words":[{"d":"सःराक्षसः","m":"that Rakshasa"},{"d":"वानरान्","m":"at Vanaras"},{"d":"मोहयित्वा","m":"hoodwinking"},{"d":"प्रतियातः","m":"withdrew"},{"d":"महाबाहो","m":"mighty armed"},{"d":"तांजनकात्मजाम्","m":"that Janaki"},{"d":"मायामयीम्","m":"illusion"},{"d":"विद्दि","m":"may know"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"चैत्यंनिकुम्भिलांनामप्राप्यहोमंकरिष्यति ।हुतवानुपयातोहिदेवैरपिसवासवैः दुराधर्षोभवत्येषसङ्ग्रामेरावणात्मजः ।","trans":"\"Ravana's son will be reaching a sanctuary named Nikumbhilam and doing a sacrificial ritual. On returning from there it will be difficult even for Indra and Devas to be at him in war. He has done this conjuring trick.","words":[{"d":"एषः","m":"in that manner"},{"d":"रावणात्मजः","m":"Ravana's son"},{"d":"निकुम्भिलांनाम","m":"by name Nikumbhilam"},{"d":"चैत्यम्","m":"sanctuary"},{"d":"प्राप्य","m":"reaching"},{"d":"होमम्","m":"sacrifice"},{"d":"करिष्यति","m":"will be doing"},{"d":"हुतावान्","m":"who can kill"},{"d":"उपयातः","m":"conjuring trick"},{"d":"सङ्ग्रामे","m":"in war"},{"d":"सवासवैः","m":"Indra"},{"d":"देवैरपि","m":"even Devas"},{"d":"दुराधर्षः","m":"very difficult"},{"d":"भवति","m":"will be"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"तेनमोहयतानूनमेषामायाप्रयोजिता विघ्नमन्विच्छतातत्रवानराणांपराक्रमे ।","trans":"\"Knowing the prowess of Vanaras, thinking surely that they will create obstacles for the ritual, he used the trick to keep them away (to be sad and not inclined for war).\"","words":[{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"वानराणाम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"पराक्रमे","m":"prowess"},{"d":"विघ्नम्","m":"knowing"},{"d":"तेन","m":"by that"},{"d":"नूनम्","m":"surely"},{"d":"एषा","m":"in that way"},{"d":"माया","m":"trick"},{"d":"प्रयोजिता","m":"using"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"ससैन्यास्तत्रगच्छामोयावत्तन्नसमाप्यते त्यजेमंनरशार्दूलमिथ्यासन्तापगतम् ।सीदतेहिबलंसर्वंदृष्टवात्वांशोककर्शितम्","trans":"\"O tiger among men! We shall go there with the army before the completion of the sacrificial ritual. Give up false agony and the cause of sorrow. Seeing you all the troops are distressed.\"","words":[{"d":"नरशार्दूलः","m":"tiger among men"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"यावत्","m":"whole thing"},{"d":"न समाप्यते","m":"before completing"},{"d":"ससैन्याः","m":"that army"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"गच्छामः","m":"go"},{"d":"आगतम्","m":"went"},{"d":"इमम्","m":"this"},{"d":"मिथ्यासन्तापम्","m":"false agony"},{"d":"त्यज","m":"giving up"},{"d":"शोककर्शितम्","m":"cause of sorrow"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"all"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"troops"},{"d":"सीदतेहि","m":"distressed"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"ससैन्यास्तत्रगच्छामोयावत्तन्नसमाप्यते त्यजेमंनरशार्दूलमिथ्यासन्तापगतम् ।सीदतेहिबलंसर्वंदृष्टवात्वांशोककर्शितम्","trans":"\"O tiger among men! We shall go there with the army before the completion of the sacrificial ritual. Give up false agony and the cause of sorrow. Seeing you all the troops are distressed.\"","words":[{"d":"नरशार्दूलः","m":"tiger among men"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"यावत्","m":"whole thing"},{"d":"न समाप्यते","m":"before completing"},{"d":"ससैन्याः","m":"that army"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"गच्छामः","m":"go"},{"d":"आगतम्","m":"went"},{"d":"इमम्","m":"this"},{"d":"मिथ्यासन्तापम्","m":"false agony"},{"d":"त्यज","m":"giving up"},{"d":"शोककर्शितम्","m":"cause of sorrow"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"all"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"troops"},{"d":"सीदतेहि","m":"distressed"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"इहत्वंस्वस्थहृदयस्तिष्ठसत्त्वसमुच्छ्रितः ।लक्ष्मणंप्रेषयास्माभिस्सहसैन्यानुकर्षिभिः","trans":"\"You be confident at heart and be courageous now. Send Lakshmana with us with the army.\"","words":[{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"स्वस्थहृदयः","m":"confident at heart"},{"d":"सत्त्वसमुच्छ्रितः","m":"be courageous"},{"d":"इह","m":"now"},{"d":"तिष्ठ","m":"stay"},{"d":"सैन्यानुकर्षिभिः","m":"along with army"},{"d":"अस्माभिःसह","m":"with us"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणम्","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"प्रेषय","m":"send"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"एषतंनरशार्दूलोरावणिंनिशितैश्शरैः ।त्याजयिष्यतितत्कर्मततोवध्योभविष्यति","trans":"\"The tiger among mortals with his sharp arrows will dispel Ravana's son from doing the action (sacrifice) then killing him will be possible.","words":[{"d":"नरशार्दूलः","m":"tiger among mortals"},{"d":"एषः","m":"in that way"},{"d":"निशितैः","m":"sharp"},{"d":"शरैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"रावणिम्","m":"Ravana's son"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"कर्म","m":"action"},{"d":"त्याजयिष्यति","m":"will dispel from doing"},{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"भविष्यति","m":"will be possible"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"तस्यैतेनिशितास्तीक्ष्णाःपत्रिपत्राङ्गवाजिनः ।पतत्रिणइवासौम्याश्शराःपास्यन्तिशोणितम्","trans":"\"Those whetted and pointed arrows fixed with limbs of birds in the form of feathers will drink his (Indrajith's) blood like cruel birds.\"","words":[{"d":"निशिताः","m":"whetted"},{"d":"एते","m":"those"},{"d":"शराः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"पतत्रिणःइवः","m":"like birds"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"शोणितम्","m":"blood"},{"d":"पास्यन्ति","m":"drink"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"सत्सन्द